revision.text:
{{tracking category}} 
{{hidden category}}

This is a tracking category for disambiguation pages. It enables us to use <code><nowiki>{{PAGESINCATEGORY:All article disambiguation pages}}</nowiki></code> to get the exact number of disambiguation pages in the main namespace.

Pages are put in this category by templates such as {{tl|Disambiguation}} and {{tl|Airport disambiguation}}. That is, templates built with the {{tl|dmbox}} meta-template, which is doing the actual categorising.

This category only lists pages in main (article) space.

== See also ==

* [[:Category:All disambiguation pages]] – Lists disambig pages in all namespaces.
* [[:Category:All set index articles]] – The corresponding category for set index articles.

